## Report Rules

- State files contain facts and decisions, not placeholders.
- Agent reports stay compact in orchestrator context.
- Long reasoning and reproduction detail belongs in handoff files.
- `lessons` are task-local; `memoryLessons` are durable only when the installed project enables that workflow.
